@startuml
title Robustness - View Active / Upcoming Meetups

left to right direction
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "Boundary Layer" {
  object "MeetupListView\n<<boundary>>" as B
}

rectangle "Control Layer" {
  object "MeetupController\n<<control>>" as C
  object "MeetupService\n<<control>>" as S
}

rectangle "Entity Layer" {
  object "Meetup\n<<entity>>" as M
  object "Location\n<<entity>>" as L
}

rectangle "External" {
  object "MeetupRepository\n<<entity>>" as R
}

B -> C : 1 openMeetupList(filters)
C -> S : 2 getActiveUpcoming(filters)
S -> R : 3 listMeetups(filters)
R -> S : 4 meetups
S -> M : 5 sortFilterByTimeDistance()
S -> C : 6 result(meetupList)
C -> B : 7 displayMeetups()

note bottom
User browses meetups. Controller requests list from service, which fetches meetups,
applies filtering/sorting (time, distance, activity), and returns a list to display.
end note

@enduml